trans-unit.source: Represents a <xref uid="langword_csharp_ScriptingScriptResourceHandler" name="ScriptingScriptResourceHandler" href=""></xref> configuration section in the <xref uid="langword_csharp_<scripting>" name="<scripting>" href=""></xref> element of the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en <xref uid="langword_csharp_ScriptingScriptResourceHandler" name="ScriptingScriptResourceHandler" href=""> </xref> konfigurasjonsdelen i den <xref uid="langword_csharp_<scripting>" name="<scripting>" href=""> </xref> elementet i konfigurasjonsfilen.

trans-unit.source: Use this type to get or set whether caching or compression is enabled for ECMAScript (JavaScript) files that are embedded as resources in an assembly.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne til å hente eller angi om hurtigbufring eller komprimering er aktivert for ECMAScript (JavaScript)-filer som er innebygd som ressurser i en samling.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ScriptingScriptResourceHandlerSection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ScriptingScriptResourceHandlerSection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets whether caching is enabled for script files that are embedded as resources in an assembly.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir om hurtigbufring er aktivert for skriptfiler som er innebygd som ressurser i en samling.

trans-unit.source: The EnableCaching property gets or sets the value for caching the results of the embedded script file, for caching any potential localization objects, and for caching scripts.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen EnableCaching henter eller angir verdien for bufring av resultatene av den innebygde skriptfilen for bufring av alle mulige lokalisering-objekter og for bufring av skript.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if caching is enabled for script files that are embedded as resources in an assembly; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis hurtigbufring er aktivert for skriptfiler som er innebygd som ressurser i en samling; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
Gets or sets whether compression is enabled for script files that are embedded as resources in an assembly.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir om komprimering er aktivert for skriptfiler som er innebygd som ressurser i en samling.

trans-unit.source: The EnableCompression property gets or sets the value that indicates whether the following will be compressed: - Script files that are embedded as resources in an assembly.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen EnableCompression henter eller angir verdien som angir om følgende komprimeres:-skriptfiler som er innebygd som ressurser i en samling.

trans-unit.source: - Localization objects, such as string resources that are contained in a resource file (.resx).
trans-unit.target: -Lokalisering objekter, for eksempel strengressursene som finnes i en ressursfil (RESX).

trans-unit.source: - Scripts that are served by the script resource handler.
> [!NOTE] > If the requesting browser does not support compression, this property has no effect.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Ber om nettleseren ikke støtter komprimering, denne egenskapen har ingen virkning hvis.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if compression is enabled for script files that are embedded as resources in an assembly; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis komprimering er aktivert for skriptfiler som er innebygd som ressurser i en samling; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
